<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">if &#40;apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.timer == 0&#41; &#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.timer = &#40;apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.period &lt;&lt; 1&#41; | 0x001;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.sequencer = &#40;apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.sequencer + 1&#41; &amp; 0x07;<br />&#125; else &#123;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; apuChannels&#91;ch&#93;.timer -= 1;<br />&#125;</div></div>

